what they remind you of.

78
00:06:20,381 --> 00:06:22,050
Okay?

79
00:06:38,816 --> 00:06:40,234
A banana.

80
00:06:46,491 --> 00:06:47,909
A swamp.

81
00:06:57,460 --> 00:06:59,295
An Afro.

82
00:07:05,843 --> 00:07:07,261
Mm-hmm.

83
00:07:18,064 --> 00:07:21,067
